  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-widget=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"544078626\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5614583333333333\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"960\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;border: 0px none;height: 389.766px;width: 694px;max-width: 100%;border-radius: 4px;display: inline-block;aspect-ratio: 1.78056 / 1;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b97a4ea1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fow6przZuPIFQiap9KCmWAicf4tzDapgLoWicKWjVgPvXRyO5jeNX4QjpbV5qGbfPacYUPFhgBP6qKSpH5zB79Dnmw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight:400;letter-spacing:1px;display:inline !important;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;float:none;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\">Meta首席执行官马克·扎克伯格</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:right;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 16px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">文丨腾讯科技特约编译&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">无忌</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:right;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">编辑丨晓静</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Meta正在加速调整人工智能战略。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">12月9日，知情人士透露，Meta原计划于2025年底发布的下一代前沿模型“牛油果”（Avocado）已被推迟至2026年第一季度，且更倾向以闭源形式推出。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这意味着Meta自2023年推出Llama系列以来的开源路线正面临逆转。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">尽管官方坚持“模型按计划推进”，但多位公司匿名工程师指出，Avocado在训练稳定性与推理泛化方面尚未达到商用层级，内部对它的发布时间窗口做出了更保守的重新评估。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这次延期象征着Meta正从过去两年强调的“开源与开放生态”转向更具防御性和商业导向的策略。随着Llama架构在外部被复刻、Llama 4反响平淡，以及OpenAI、谷歌、Anthropic接连抬升前沿模型门槛，Meta越来越难在开源体系中保持竞争优势。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Meta首席执行官马克·扎克伯格（Mark Zuckberg）在2025年夏天曾明确暗示，公司必须“严格减轻风险”，这被内部视为关闭开源窗口的前兆。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为了支撑闭源模型的算力需求，Meta在最新财报中将2025年资本支出上调至700–720亿美元，重点投向训练集群与数据中心扩建，包括为Meta超级智能实验室（Superintelligence Labs，MSL）打造的“普罗米修斯”（Prometheus）超大规模数据中心。内部人士称，这项投入“相当于重建公司的AI地基”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><mark style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"></mark><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:20px;\">01内部震荡与新领导层：从开源文化到“工业化AI”的组织重排</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-widget=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"544078625\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.55625\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"960\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;border: 0px none;height: 385.43px;width: 694px;max-width: 100%;border-radius: 4px;display: inline-block;aspect-ratio: 1.80056 / 1;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=006acbca&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fow6przZuPIFQiap9KCmWAicf4tzDapgLoWtEC44QjyDz9b8m2ibNy1N2crrvRe90jz1I9NTcAjMyZ2fxFE8EZiaUBg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight:400;letter-spacing:1px;display:inline !important;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;float:none;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight:400;letter-spacing:1px;display:inline !important;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;float:none;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\">MSL负责人汪滔</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Avocado的延迟只是表象，真正的变化发生在组织深处。随着Llama 4未能达到预期，公司AI领导层经历了多年未见的剧烈更替：FAIR与GenAI的主导权被削弱，传统学术导向的研发体系让位于强调产品落地与闭环速度的MSL。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这一轮重排因扎克伯格大规模引入外部高端人才而加速。通过与Scale AI的143亿美元交易，Meta将其创始人汪滔(Alexandr Wang)纳入核心决策链条，由他领导精英化的MSL，Avocado的开发就集中在该实验室。汪滔及其团队带来了与Meta常年文化完全不同的一套工作方法：闭环管理、减少跨组输入、高压节奏以及强调“先做Demo，别写报告”（Demo, don’t memo）的工程风格。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这套节奏与FAIR的开放式研究文化冲撞强烈。多位Meta员工指出，以前的Meta重视跨团队评审与透明共享，而现在的MSL更像“公司内部的封闭创业公司”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-widget=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"544078628\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"960\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;border: 0px none;height: 387.594px;width: 694px;max-width: 100%;border-radius: 4px;display: inline-block;aspect-ratio: 1.7905 / 1;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=34765df4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fow6przZuPIFQiap9KCmWAicf4tzDapgLoWMBxXRwjtCUBGyvV6fltYmMcaQBr7UKrnAnOSl6uk32WOsRvxWI2mgQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight:400;letter-spacing:1px;display:inline !important;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;float:none;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight:400;letter-spacing:1px;display:inline !important;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;float:none;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\">即将离职的首席AI科学家杨立昆（Yann LeCun）</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在最新的组织调整中，AI相关团队出现多轮重组与裁撤，FAIR的部分研究方向被缩减，600多名与基础研究相关的人员被裁撤，直接促使首席AI科学家杨立昆（Yann LeCun）宣布将离职创业。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">过去依靠协作与学术氛围推进模型研发的模式，正在被一种“工程先行、商业优先”的体系取代。新的AI领导层将重点放在模型能力的产品化、推理优化和安全控制，而非追求开源影响力。在内部讨论中，“开源是否已完成使命”成为最常被提及的冲突话题之一。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><mark style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"></mark><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:20px;\">02硬件路线图调整：元宇宙退居次席，AI成新核心叙事</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-widget=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"544078627\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"960\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;border: 0px none;height: 387.594px;width: 694px;max-width: 100%;border-radius: 4px;display: inline-block;aspect-ratio: 1.7905 / 1;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=24b3c133&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fow6przZuPIFQiap9KCmWAicf4tzDapgLoWQxicgkvRJhSQPcaGf8n8sTZ3NFEUtdUJtXZxdfZLGujER3UTTXMjCMQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight:400;letter-spacing:1px;display:inline !important;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;float:none;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight:400;letter-spacing:1px;display:inline !important;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;float:none;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\">Meta推迟发布XR眼镜至2027年</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI战略重排也迅速波及Meta的硬件路线图。公司2025年启动了对硬件部门Reality Labs的全面审查，多个增强现实XR原型项目被降级或暂停，Quest系列的未来迭代节奏明显放缓。Meta计划在未来两年逐步削减元宇宙预算，把资源重心转向与AI模型直接协同的智能眼镜、语音助手和本地推理设备。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">内部文件显示，下一代自研ASIC推理芯片可能提前量产，其目标不是服务虚拟世界，而是加速闭源前沿模型的终端推理效率。Meta工程团队被要求重新定义芯片的矩阵计算性能与显存带宽，围绕Avocado和后续模型构建定制加速路径。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在基础设施层面，Meta也在从“自建为主”转向更务实的混合模式。该公司已同CoreWeave、甲骨文和Blue Owl Capital进一步扩大合作规模，并推动270亿美元的“Hyperion”数据中心计划，以填补闭源模型部署所需的高强度算力缺口。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">多位员工形容，这一轮调整“意味着元宇宙时代的终结”。曾经作为战略核心的Reality Labs，如今不得不把更多资源和带宽让位给AI。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><mark style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"></mark><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:20px;\">03一场横跨技术、组织与资本的全面转向</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Avocado的延期不仅是一项研发进度调整，而是Meta战略方向清晰转折的外化信号。在开源优势被竞争对手快速消解、内部组织被迫重整、市场要求加速兑现投资回报的三重压力下，Meta正在从根本上重写其 AI发展路径：从研发文化到组织架构，从硬件规划到资本投入，所有关键要素都在围绕“闭源前沿模型”重构为一个更封闭、更集中、更以商业结果为导向的体系。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这不是一次普通的方向微调，而是继2012年全面拥抱移动互联网、2020年押注元宇宙之后，Meta十多年来的第三次战略大迁徙。不同的是，前两次转向由外部趋势驱动，而这一次，则是Meta在激烈竞争环境中不得不做出的生存式选择，其范围之广与牵涉层级之深，已远超以往。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">一名参与Avocado项目的工程师总结得更直接：“我们已经从‘讨论未来’转向‘争取领先’。现在的Meta，不是追愿景，而是在用全部资源确保不会被时代甩下。”</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Meta 正经历从开源到闭源的 AI 战略转变，次代模型 Avocado 延期，组织架构重组，元宇宙让位于 AI，以应对激烈竞争，确保商业回报。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Meta 正经历从开源到闭源的 AI 战略转变，次代模型 Avocado 延期，组织架构重组，元宇宙让位于 AI，以应对激烈竞争，确保商业回报。",
  "summary": "文章深入分析了 Meta 在 AI 战略上的重大调整，由过去的开源路线转向更具防御性和商业导向的闭源策略。具体体现在新一代前沿模型“牛油果”（Avocado）的延期发布并倾向闭源，以及由 Llama 4 反响平淡引发的内部组织震荡：FAIR 和 GenAI 的主导权被削弱，强调产品落地和闭环速度的 MSL 崛起。在硬件层面，元宇宙项目被降级，资源重心转向 AI 协同的智能眼镜和本地推理设备。这一切都源于 Meta 面对 OpenAI、谷歌等竞争对手的压力，旨在通过更集中的资源投入、更高效的组织管理和更大规模的资本支出，确保前沿 AI 模型能力的产品化和商业化，被视为 Meta 十多年来第三次重大战略迁徙。",
